testCase.name: Home component renders the title "Quiz App"
Home component contains a Play button
<QuizSummary /> displays no statistics available message when state is undefined
<QuizSummary /> displays quiz summary when state is defined
<QuizSummary /> renders the correct remark for a score of 0%
<QuizSummary /> renders the correct remark for a score between 1% and 30%
<QuizSummary /> renders the correct remark for a score between 31% and 50%
<QuizSummary /> renders the correct remark for a score between 51% and 70%
<QuizSummary /> renders the correct remark for a score between 71% and 84%
<QuizSummary /> renders the correct remark for a score of 85% or higher
<QuizSummary /> displays Play Again and Back to Home buttons when state is defined
<QuizSummary /> redirects to Play Quiz page when Play Again button is clicked
